  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to tap at any place of a row with a checkbox so it will be selected without extra hustle.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\nIn the current implementation, you have to make a precise tap to a checkbox which is not convenient.\r\nIt's better to expand an tap zone to the whole row for lists elements with checkboxes. \r\n\r\nThis functionality could be found in the following cases:\r\n1. Choosing members for group chats\r\n2. Adding member to a group chat\r\n3. Filtering transaction history\r\n4. Managing assets screen in the wallet\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nIncreased tap zone for rows with checkboxes\r\n<img width=\"439\" alt=\"screenshot 2018-03-01 11 19 18\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6559881/36839463-71466594-1d42-11e8-92ac-db4e6409993c.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nSmall tap zone for rows with checkboxes\r\n<img width=\"460\" alt=\"screenshot 2018-03-01 11 19 22\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6559881/36839478-7d4fcbfa-1d42-11e8-8753-5dfeb9e3e49c.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n### Choosing members for group chats\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Tap the plus button on the home screen\r\n- Tap the Start group chat button\r\n\r\n### Adding member to a group chat\r\n- In the created group chat 3 dots in the right corner\r\n- Choose Group info\r\n- Tap Add members\r\n\r\n### Filtering transaction history\r\n- Choose wallet tab on the tab bar\r\n- Tap Transaction History\r\n- Tap 3 lines icon in the right corner\r\n\r\n### Managing assets screen in the wallet\r\n- Choose wallet tab on the tab bar\r\n- Tap 3 dots in the right corner of the screen\r\n- Choose Manage assets",
